header: Test vector of type HkdfTest are intended for the verification of HKDF.

notes.EmptySalt: An empty salt is a valid input for HKDF. It is equivalent to a salt with n zero bytes, where n is the size of the underlying hash function.
notes.SizeTooLarge: The output size of HKDF is limited to 255*size of the hash digest
